sub_title: EVP Sustainability & Climate - Lead Paris Alignment at Rabobank
summary: Leading Rabobank's climate impact strategy, including our commitment to reach Net Zero in 2050. In addition to developing and coordinating the bank's overall approach to Paris Alignment, my work includes evaluating and selecting carbon accounting methodologies, decarbonization pathways and target-setting tools for different asset classes; working with frontline business units to develop climate portfolio optimization strategies for key economic sectors; co-developing and managing climate data gathering and analysis together with our Sustainable Data and Climate Risk teams; advising on climate stress testing; managing the production of our flagship climate report; and representing the bank on different (inter)national climate initiatives.
